# Experimental 64-bit (wine64) rootfs + wasm. Too big for GitHub's free LFS
# budget, so these are NOT committed — they live on local disk and wrangler
# uploads them straight to Cloudflare Pages at deploy time. Regenerate from the
# Boxedwine64 build (see public/64/README.md). The small text files (html, js,
# css, manifests) ARE committed.
public/64/*.wasm
public/64/*.zip
public/64/*.part*
